ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實有人會打下機啊 追下switch ps4咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買d驚番去打下？"},{"pid":"ad499ff03c1db4d900f8e10d9858343afc86c286","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者咁講<br />\n你唔一定要好detail咁share你既background比同事<br />\n不過你要比到d野對方感興趣，會想同你做朋友既<br />\n<br />\n例如佢地問你平時放假有咩做<br />\n你話我乜都唔做架自閉 = Deadair<br />\n你話我會同d叔伯去船P同姐妹去High tea = 又deadair<br />\n你話我平時會去行下山，約fd行街 呢d common野 等人可以再發掘落去 咁先易溶入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我覺得你講嘅嘢好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我啱啱入職嗰陣就係答咗果啲dead air嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都好想同佢地一齊行山，但每次我話join，佢哋都會話你呢啲有錢女邊曬得邊行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時連放工話一齊食飯，佢哋都會話我哋去呢啲低檔嘢你唔啱㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過一兩次之後，我就冇再同佢地講嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下間公司，我會努力試吓學你講嘅咁答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ec2d6b602af97877d121ab06d51fdb06e362a2","tid":1046733,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"唔知你點諗啦<br />\n不過我做過幾間公司都係HI BYE FD多<br />\n大家係工作上相處OK有時都有傾有講<br />\n但放工真係無乜約出街/交流<br />\n頂多係大時大節笑下大家有無街出/約人咁<br />\n最多真係一年1-2次聚會(自己搞<br />\n反而有幾個離左職後幾FD都有KEEP contact<br />\n間唔中打下波食下飯咁<br />\n在職時都唔覺咁FD底"},{"pid":"5307e61e3d05458316fc65c9ce6a221494f38797","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f1165dc801a45a08f8692d1315a5e4e3f8ea2e7","tid":1046733,"uid":183101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"我都係咁俾人叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我咩都冇講過<br />\n佢地只係知我外國返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:09:44.000Z","msg":"係呀，以前做外資公司，啲同事九成都外國返嚟，所以冇乜特別。<br />\n但啱先呢間中資公司，啲同事就好似標籤晒所有出國嘅都好有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca8bf5fb9de623b00897c63233395514edd0715","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d607b0d00294109ee80068930972e7c7d423da9","tid":1046733,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"呢樣好講緣份<br />\n冇可能個個都同你夾咀型/岩傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:11:26.000Z","msg":"我明白啊，但係我個人鍾意熱鬧，喺公司以外都有好多朋友，但大部份時間都喺公司，個心理更加唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e19708666c378e1b638e2ab6e8255ae87402fd","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb38ca862a797c7daa0ce16801c34230d88dd97","tid":1046733,"uid":71526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"係邊頭返工？有機會一齊lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n職場上係咁，做好自己就好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:12:57.000Z","msg":"多謝你呀巴打，希望新公司有轉變，btw港島返工"},{"pid":"22f236b744b112d27759bbd929f7dc5bb062f259","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1adc2d234d0a80d5750f66dcb4d1e209b70bbb","tid":1046733,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:50:23.000Z","msg":"咁你應該搵返d 外資公司<br />\n大家同聲同氣<br />\n有d 人容易埋到堆，我自己就做幾份工都覺得好難埋堆<br />\n依家都唔強求<br />\n傾得埋咪講多兩句"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"係呀所以我嚟緊份新工都係外資公司，中資公司真係好難融入，可能因為真係自己冇香港生活嘅經驗，好多佢哋嘅話題我都冇辦法融入(淨係講大學上莊Ocamp我已經唔知佢哋講緊乜)，我嘅生活佢哋又唔理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd2872f9a3e3e392183b8085141c5077af484fb","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7e3083f44706070d2c6659779b17fa992f2138e","tid":1046733,"uid":5627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"