"uid":197841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fc017806cbbc67484bb7b3735489b168eabce49","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請同事食飯<br />\n人地問你d background 資料個時講多d<br />\n唔好乜都話唔講啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係啱啱入職嗰陣時講太多(提及左屋企做咩同住邊)佢哋就當咗/話我係有錢女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我講親咩都話我鬼妹仔、有錢女，好似仇富咁，句句有骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話我真係有錢就話啫，弊在我唔係呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />至多叫小康、中產、唔愁三餐，佢地就成日串我同排擠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以其實我暗下決定，新工唔再提background，儘量話自己窮，其實啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"you are right<br />\n<br />\n扮返佢地個level，唔係又會排擠妳"},{"pid":"3b40f1ce8357d272d1b6889101b8878548dcbbee","tid":1046733,"uid":49642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad499ff03c1db4d900f8e10d9858343afc86c286","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者咁講<br />\n你唔一定要好detail咁share你既background比同事<br />\n不過你要比到d野對方感興趣，會想同你做朋友既<br />\n<br />\n例如佢地問你平時放假有咩做<br />\n你話我乜都唔做架自閉 = Deadair<br />\n你話我會同d叔伯去船P同姐妹去High tea = 又deadair<br />\n你話我平時會去行下山，約fd行街 呢d common野 等人可以再發掘落去 咁先易溶入到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我覺得你講嘅嘢好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我啱啱入職嗰陣就係答咗果啲dead air嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我都好想同佢地一齊行山，但每次我話join，佢哋都會話你呢啲有錢女邊曬得邊行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時連放工話一齊食飯，佢哋都會話我哋去呢啲低檔嘢你唔啱㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過一兩次之後，我就冇再同佢地講嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下間公司，我會努力試吓學你講嘅咁答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"如果你上間公司既同事去到咁盡<br />\n我覺得未必係因為你入職個時唔小心透露自己中產+小康<br />\n你日常返工比人見到既表面生活都應該好唔草根<br />\n佢地先會講d咁既野<br />\n你係咪用開d名牌袋，衫，鞋<br />\n一個袋都十萬個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35ba2f15195874980cfabc35882d82ef6ecc9ab","tid":1046733,"uid":136249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T16:11:23.000Z","msg":"反而舊個份工d同事勁唔捨得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個星期五都專登搭地鐵過黎同我食lunch,係咁叫我番去個頭搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家都考慮梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而新公司多後生埋唔到堆，都同公司文化有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7aa2ac87fd0765879203cdf5374c60880c27c8","tid":1046733,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"好多時自己一個食飯咪又係咁, 返呢間美帝公司3年幾都係咁.<br />\n同同事都係叫聲早晨咁. 有時講野咪撘下咀.<br />\n呢輪就有時星期五同幾個同事出下去食飯咁<br />\n絲打仲後生大把時間, 我呢D 老鬼放工趕住返屋企湊仔,仲邊咁得閒約同事食晚飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75abbb30f727038432808d14a039493090574df","tid":1046733,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182ab7cfd1a702a95b7f52837d85dcd940f8a4b7","tid":1046733,"uid":237844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94246ea00ff4db169f92bd178ec5a78e8e79b419","tid":1046733,"uid":129644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"就咁睇 樓主最大問題係同local 香港人話題興趣太唔似 可以試下接觸多d 本地文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"有冇介紹可以點接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勤上連登算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好努力學習同睇啲熱門話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:45:46.000Z","msg":"FB/IG 